body_html:
You can see the inference time (basically 1/fps) in the debug view by pressing the volume key. So I guess you can look at that code to get an idea of what you can do. Looking at the display code here:
lines.add("Inference time: " + lastProcessingTimeMs + "ms");
It looks like you can use lastProcessingTimeMs as a starting point for your FPS.
body:
You can see the inference time (basically 1/fps) in the debug view by pressing the volume key. So I guess you can look at that code to get an idea of what you can do. Looking at the display code here:
`lines.add("Inference time: " + lastProcessingTimeMs + "ms");`
It looks like you can use `lastProcessingTimeMs` as a starting point for your FPS.
